nodes.text: In 22 BBY, this actress, a protester of the Clone Wars, starred in a holovid entitled Republic Medcenter. Her performance and the film itself were given negative reviews by Jedi Knight Anakin Skywalker and Senator Padmé Amidala. That year, the actress began dating Galactic Senator Herbin, despite his marriage to another woman, resulting in a scandal widely publicized by HoloNet News and Entertainment.
The actress was briefly mentioned in The Clone Wars: No Prisoners, which was released in 2009 and written by Karen Traviss as part of the Star Wars: The Clone Wars multimedia project.
